data.description: Completely remodeled 2 Family Home in Schenectady. Home features 3 bedrooms and 1 bath on each floor. Hardwood floors throughout the house. Brand new kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Gorgeous bathroom with floor to ceiling tile. New plumbing, electric, heating system and hot water tanks. Off street parking with a 2 car detached garage offers plenty of storage space. Rent one unit while living in the other. This is a perfect property with nothing left to do!
